<br>
But what if we started using these new abilities to pull bigger and more exciting battles.<br>
<br>
For exmple, say you are fighting in the Hole. The Hole is all about crowd controll, right? <br>
<br>
Well, what if you drag along a chaman and a cleric, a few melee who can toe to toe a mob (Warrior/Pally/SK/Ranger). Pull comes inc. hybrids peel off and directly engage the mobs. Shaman slows the mobs on the hybrids first while the cleric heals the Warrior. If everyone is taking damage, the cleric utilizes their group heals to keep everyone afloat. If you have a nuker (or god forbid an AoE in that hellish place) they can be adding damage as well. The exp would be fast.<br>
